{"tid":423183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N件以前成日做而家唔再做既事","createTime":"2017-10-03T16:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T18:13:40.000Z","uid":148528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0581dbceb93a8fa15d88072da47ec4f02320212e","tid":423183,"uid":148528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"1.MSN<br />\n學生時代真係好沉迷MSN，每日放學返到屋企就傾到訓覺，係個Mon前面一路等人Online甚至係等女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有佢啲小遊戲（踩地雷）<br />\n<br />\n2.傾通頂<br />\n唔係講緊面對面個種（雖然而家都好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ）<br />\n係講緊煲電話粥煲通宵個啲，傾成6，7個鐘然後一齊傾住電腦睇日出個種感覺真係...唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.駁三線<br />\n同啲fd一齊駁三線講是非又係好正，甚至駁電話打133比女神為左聽佢把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4.SMS<br />\n以前限住數據甚至識朋友第一件事就係問左對方電話咩台，睇下SMS洗唔洗錢，仲好記得用緊儲值卡既年代有次同個同學表白完電話咁啱無哂錢真係屌左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人愈大科技愈發達就冇哂呢啲回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515f0179e1b4d9e5ca09c61ce9bb209b7280f97f","tid":423183,"uid":34444,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:40:42.000Z","msg":"拖老母隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1c20e6e72333bdb2502bde30f3fab27b5eef64","tid":423183,"uid":36049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:41:18.000Z","msg":"Post ig"},{"pid":"d5a52a6114ee0b34006cdceb5807e62cc7750951","tid":423183,"uid":73694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"打丁"},{"pid":"da57df8d715f4ee13407eec79a4812d612196c68","tid":423183,"uid":104256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"功課"},{"pid":"42fa7324d93f413f8fc93ab9d79606f545ed5d3f","tid":423183,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply